{"tid":56643,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩date左個女仔，唔太清楚邊到出錯","createTime":"2016-12-27T11:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T16:56:58.000Z","uid":50286,"like":11,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc0217b3ca750d968ab9771ae0585440d88661a","tid":56643,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"我已經30歲左右，後生個陣好迷動漫好鐘意打機，成間房都係周邊同埋cushion，最激試過anime飛機杯，所以身邊既人一路都離我好遠，怕比我毒親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左近年兩老已經開始頂唔順係咁叫我搵個伴，話好想湊下孫咁，咁就係咁介紹姑婆個孫呀，外叔公個女比我識⋯<br />\n<br />\n但係可能係我個樣啦，所以我都冇咩收鑊，到依家都係青頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我自己覺得我都算正常樣又有米八既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能唯一缺點係內向少少？<br />\n<br />\n上個星期大姨丈介紹左個世姪女比我識，佢斯斯文文做護士既，都幾靚女有少少波咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢就約左今日食晏啦，我同佢去左間幾好既餐廳（對我黎講都幾貴個食評網話差唔多二百五一個人）<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就叫左個沙津,我就叫左個扒咁<br />\n<br />\n咁我就問佢夠唔夠食架 乜肉都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話我慣架啦我係個virgitarian黎⋯<br />\n<br />\n我雖然冇去過外國讀書，但係我都有係av網search過virgin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐係處女咁既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就話哦，咁你搵岩人啦我係個virgin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪好岩你口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢打左我一把就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩大姨丈仲打電話比我問我做咩激佢個世姪女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853b6e6c9c1b71b5609d24e3acbaf85c50ac51b6","tid":56643,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩激我個女"},{"pid":"2c71ffbc98e757d2e606f17635a471aef691b389","tid":56643,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1d7b0bc1a997a26114f99176a75a7c5dc7dc60b","tid":56643,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15b3cfde9485b5c3cc4ef9288f207f4fc5d13e1f","tid":56643,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"負評，上一頁"},{"pid":"ca64ff725bdfa9f42a809e93ebc37bcac59ff515","tid":56643,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩激我個女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口口"},{"pid":"4f6415de342cbef6b1165472918a96304c1bafab","tid":56643,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩激我個女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明佢做咩咁燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126eabbbc4c0583f07f182dc17bf47098f2beb8a","tid":56643,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好笑 重作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題黎唔係想好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7143a9c46f09f66113fc8c7c31226fa44bc3ce72","tid":56643,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生有何歡<br />\n死有何懼<br />\n<br />\n生亦何苦<br />\n死亦何哀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係唔係可以係到搵到答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e